lead_paragraph: The International Cricket Council has criticized West Indies for using their victory speech at the World Twenty20 tournament to complain about their cricket board after a long drawn-out pay dispute.

headline.print_headline: Cricket: ICC Blasts Windies for World T20 Outburst Over Pay
